array.item: Are You Afraid of the Dark?

array.name: descript_array
array.item: The adventures of a new generation of Warner Bros. Looney Tunes characters.
A boy named Bobby Generic creates adventures using his overactive imagination
The Dark Knight battles crime in Gotham City with occasional help from Robin and Batgirl.
Follows the misadventures of four irreverent grade-schoolers in the quiet, dysfunctional town of South Park, Colorado.
Two demoted fighter pilots battle evil as high flying masked vigilantes.
Fry, a pizza guy, is accidentally frozen in 1999 and thawed out New Year\'s Eve 2999.
A team of mutant superheroes fight for justice and human acceptance in the Marvel Comics universe.
A young man with spider-like abilities fights crime as a superhero in New York City while trying to have a normal personal life.

The offbeat adventures of Courage, a cowardly dog who must overcome his own fears to heroically defend his unknowing farmer owners from all kinds of dangers, paranormal events and menaces that appear around their land.
In a wacky Rhode Island town, a dysfunctional family strive to cope with everyday life as they are thrown from one crazy scenario to another.
The last son of the planet Krypton protects his adoptive home of Earth as the greatest of the superheroes
The misadventures of a talking sea sponge who works at a fast food restaurant under the sea.
A straight laced propane salesman in Arlen, Texas tries to deal with the wacky antics of his family and friends, while also trying to keep his son in line.
The cartoon misadventures of four babies and their snotty older cousin as they face the things in life they don\'t understand.
Animated MTV series about two teenage heavy-metal music fans who occasionally do idiotic things because they\'re bored. For them, everything is "cool" or "sucks."

The everyday life of Arnold, a 4th-grader in a nameless city that resembles Brooklyn, New York, who lives in a multi-racial boarding house with his grandparents and a motley assortment of neighbors and friends.
Three super-powered little girls constantly save the world (or at least the city of Townsville) from monsters, would-be conquerers and a few other gross things.
Ensemble cast of off-the-wall Warner Brothers characters, appearing in a wide variety of roles.
The life of a young boy as he meets friends, falls in love, maneuvers his way through grade 6 and writes all about it in his journal.
The misadventures of a boy genius and his annoying sister.
A smart and cynical girl goes through teenage life as a proud outsider in a world of mainly idiotic adolescents and condescending adults.
The off-the-wall, day-to-day life of three friends who have exactly the same name.
The gross misadventures of a hyper chihuahua and a stupid cat.
A genius mouse and his stupid sidekick try to conquer the world each night.
The wacky misadventures of an Australian wallaby and his friends as he finishes his transition to American life.
The misadventures of a dumb blond egomanaic who is deluded about his own manliness.
Four friends and their daily lives of playing extreme sports, surfing, and getting into some crazy situations.
A bumbling superhero battles crime with the help of his daughter and pilot sidekick.
The wacky and sometimes surreal adventures of Norbert and Daggett Beaver.
Baloo the Bear from the Jungle Book is cast as a 1930\'s Pacific Islands bush pilot.
A divorced father, he has custody of his 23-year-old slacker son Ben, who dreams of wealth and freedom but is too lazy to find a real job
Space Ghost in his 40s is no longer a superhero, and now he even goes by his real name Tad Ghostal.
Jay Sherman is a New York film critic who has to review films he doesn\'t like for a living.
About a 6 years old kid name Shin-chan who is always create havoc with people around him. He also have a taste with older woman.
The adventures of Ash Ketchum and his partner Pikachu, who travel across many regions in hopes of being regarded as a Pokemon master.
Disney\'s fun-loving chipmunks are reimagined as the leaders of a team of detectives/crime-fighters, rounding out the team are two mice, Gadget Hackwrench and Monterey Jack and Zipper, a fly.

Life is a difficult challenge for Mr Bean, who despite being a grown adult, has trouble completing even the simplest of tasks. Thankfully, his perseverance is usually rewarded, and he finds an ingenious way around the problem.
The Hanna-Barbera-created Oscar-winning cat-and-mouse team of Tom & Jerry returned to TV in an hour-long stretch of new adventures.
The Pink Panther is a heroic, moral cartoon cat with pink fur and the manners of an English aristocrat. He only becomes flustered or angry at obtuse or offensive humans
Stories about Garfield the cat, Odie the dog, their owner Jon and the trouble they get into, and Orson the Pig and his adventures on a farm with fellow farm animals.
The misadventures of two modern-day Stone Age families, the Flintstones and the Rubbles.
The adventures of a quartet of humanoid warrior turtles and their friends.
Comic tales of a group of good friends, 4 boys and 2 girls, during breaks in primary school, as they grow up, relate to each other, and have brushes with authority.
The program focuses on the misadventures of two unlikely yet somehow biological siblings: Cow and Chicken.
The satiric adventures of a working-class family in the misfit city of Springfield.
A samurai sent through time fights to return home and save the world.

The Banks family, a respectable Californian family, take in a relative - Will Smith, a street-smart teenager from Philadelphia. The idea is to make him respectable, responsible and mature, but Will has got other plans
An amiable man teaches preschool subjects with his puppet friends with games, songs and the infinite number of costumes inside his tickle trunk.
After learning that he is from another planet, a warrior named Goku and his friends are prompted to defend it from an onslaught of extraterrestrial enemies.
Scientist/comedian Bill Nye explores various aspects of science for young viewers.
Kermit the Frog and his friends struggle to put on a weekly variety show.
An intelligent and witty dog imagines himself in the role of characters from classic books and gets involved in similar real-life adventures.
A group of kids get together in the woods, and tell ghost stories.
A squadron of giant robot pilots of a beleaguered Earth colony bring the war to their oppressive home planet.
On a special inner city street, the inhabitants, both human and puppet, teach preschool subjects with comedy, cartoons, games and songs.
Follows the struggles of three young ninjas - Naruto Uzumaki, Sasuke Uchiha and Sakura Haruno - as they go through their training.
The globe-trotting treasure-hunting money-making adventures of billionaire Scrooge McDuck and his nephews.
A group of toadlets (young toads) find themselves trapped in a forest after missing the migration to Toad Hollow
Pee-Wee Herman and his friends have wacky, imaginative fun in his unique playhouse.
Tales of horror based on the gruesome E.C. comic books of the 1950s.
Two opposing factions of transforming alien robots engage in a battle that has the fate of Earth in the balance.
An eccentric school-teacher takes her class on wondrous educational field trips with the help of a magical school bus.
